<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ح ر ز:</span> <span class="c2">(الْحِرْزُ)</span> الْمَوْضِعُ الْحَصِينُ،<span class="c5"> يُقَالُ:</span> هَذَا <span class="c2">(حِرْزٌ حَرِيزٌ)</span> وَيُسَمَّى التَّعْوِيذُ <span class="c2">(حِرْزًا)</span> . وَ <span class="c2">(احْتَرَزَ)</span> مِنْ كَذَا وَ <span class="c2">(تَحَرَّزَ)</span> مِنْهُ أَيْ تَوَقَّاهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>